channel.title: Practicing Jad
channel.description: Hello guys, I recently started playing runescape again with the 07 update and one of the biggest things im lacking atm is a fire cape. I have never known how to do jad and i realize you can look at vids but i was wondering if anyone had a server with 07 graphics and a shorter version (or just jad) of fight caves. If an admin does not have this but would be willing to set it up for me.
